"1 1/2 tablespoons all-purpose flour, plus more for dusting","1 pound all-butter puff pastry","1  Granny Smith apple, peeled and coarsely grated","1  Pink Lady apple, peeled and coarsely grated","3 tablespoons sugar, plus more for dusting","1/2 cup farmer cheese","1/8 teaspoon cinnamon","1 pinch of salt","1  (large) egg, beaten"